{"id":607,"date":"2021-03-28T15:44:41","date_gmt":"2021-03-28T15:44:41","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/?p=607"},"modified":"2021-03-28T15:44:43","modified_gmt":"2021-03-28T15:44:43","slug":"goa-sunrise-and-more-only-in-hollant-beach","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/goa-sunrise-and-more-only-in-hollant-beach\/","title":{"rendered":"Goa Sunrise And More Only In Hollant Beach"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Hollant Beach in Goa is one amongst the well-known beaches of Goa where every year it attracts many visitors from around the world. As it is at a distance away of 7 km. from Vasco city where the beach is exactly located in the Mormugao Taluka. Though from Bogmalo beach its at a 1.5 km distance away. Among all other beaches in Goa, this is the only beach where you can see the sunrise. What enticing part is how it settled by the shallow bay that has a gentle slope towards the sea and still look so beautiful. And again one more reason to love about the beach is that there are no currents flowing here so for tourists who longed for some serious swimming at the beach is very safe. Though during low tide, the beach area heavily increases for&nbsp;the place is quite gradual and shallow.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You will see how the place is tucked in the foothills of the Western Ghats lush, where the beach grace visitors with unique and beautiful views. During the high tide,&nbsp;the beach looks even better and quite scenic. While this is the time when the sea water rises and mixed into the fresh waters of streams nearby. Only the sad part is that there are no major hotels are located close to the beach or any shacks for the matter. However, accommodation can be found within the local people as they serve their guest houses and villas on rent. Despite everything, the beach is well linked by roads, though no buses available Hollant Beach. If you wish to reach there only if you have to do it your own car or rented modes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Hollant Beach is very smaller in size and it is considered to be good for fishing. This Beach is peaceful, isolated while stretched beautifully in the white soft sand which definitely give&nbsp;the vibes of peace to making it an excellent opportunity to spend some time without any noise. As the other beaches of Vasco, such as Cumberthi, and Baina has become increasingly polluted, so Hollant can be considered to provides the tourists with a good alternative. Even with the choice of angling.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hollant Beach is the only place other than Grande Island where you can see plate coral growing. Where you can catch the main attraction of the coral reefs and coral plates. Even the school of fishes established at this beach where you can watch the different varieties of fisheries and other collection of aquatic animals which are totally exotic to experience. It is an isolated and completely secluded beach only is inhabited by the villagers who lives there.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best time is suggested for the visitors are from October to March.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hollant Beach in Goa is one amongst the well-known beaches of Goa where every year it attracts many visitors from around the world. As it is at a distance away of 7 km. from Vasco city where the beach is exactly located in the Mormugao Taluka. Though from Bogmalo beach its at a 1.5 km [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":609,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/607"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"